{"type": "article", "id": 22624, "title": "水边故事系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-22T10:45:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122218bkROI6ATwoFjM0hC.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是来自瑞典哥特堡大学设计工艺学院（HDK）的学生设计的家具系列，他们以水边的故事（stories by the water）为主题。圆桌  Sophie hardy 用 65 层纸制作，边缘有彩色的立体波浪，模拟出水纹的感觉。另有一款木质屏风上做出了凹凸感，在光影下也有水纹的效果。还有一款柜子上覆盖有大理石图案，搭配以拱形的结构，线条柔和有如水光。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122216cvDYuZ3EChtOFgBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77383863\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122216uqeF25thJsxSPwZQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.31173594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122217SML8DvkuiGrj6wpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21271394\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122218uZVzhBKGamvlJXx7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05012225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}